{
  "stem": "10549.4",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That was very awkward, [LAUGHS] very [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "German, mostly.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "German, Polish, but German mostly.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now after a while, I worked as an-- in a supply house for about three months.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I-- I quit because I got a offer as a painter because I had experience during the war to be a painter.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we got acquainted with some-- a paint-- paint-- contractor, a painter contractor.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he offered me a job.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the job paid almost twice as much what I was getting in the supply house.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And so I took the job as a painter.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I was doing-- doing better than at the other job, when I was working over there as a painter for six months.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And winter came, and we didn't have any job in winter time because not too many people do painting in the winter time.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And my wife uncle open up a bakery.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So I decided to go to the-- and he offered me a job in the bakery, not that I knew what I was doing.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But he gave me a job there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And 15 years later, I was still working in the bakery.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I become a baker.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And 15 years later, we were invited to a bar mitzvah, to two-- we got invitation to two bar mitzvahs.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "One was in Newark, New Jersey, where we-- where we used to live.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And the other invitation we got to Canada.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And the invitation to bar mitzvah was from a person which we spent war time in Krakow prison because we used to keep in touch, whoever survived, with the few people who survived.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "What we went through together, we kept in touch with each other because we felt like-- like a family.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
